graphql.query:
query GetRangeofLedgers  {
  blockRange(sLedger: 55778116, lLedger: 55778118) {
    ledgerSequence
    ledgerHash
    successfulTransactionCount
    failedTransactionCount
    operationCount
    previousHash
    timestamp
    transactions {
      ledgerSequence
      sourceAddress
      transactionHash
      fee
      timestamp
      memo
      isSuccessful
      sourceAccountSequence
      operations {
        ledgerSequence
        sourceAddress
        destinationAddress
        transactionHash
        assetType
        amount
        timestamp
        amount
        fee
        type
        assetTypeIssuer
      }
    }
  }
}
